==English==

===Etymology===
Spanish “The Child,” referring to the Christ child, as the phenomenon is observed around Christmas time

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[el|El]] [[niño|Niño]]'''

# An [[invasion]] of warm water into the surface of the [[Pacific Ocean]] off the coast of [[Peru]] and [[Ecuador]] every 4 to 7 years that causes changes in local and regional [[climate]].

